{
  "stem": "2581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was room to sit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, there was room to sit because, from that ghe-- from the ghetto, they tried to bring the people yet in a way not to scare us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the ghetto had [NON-ENGLISH] and other people that worked officially for the government, they were even sent in other cars-- in the passenger cars.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that-- that was very few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was just men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was just men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came to-- to Birkenau, and again the sele-- the selection started over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they were sending people to the right, to the left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Didn't know what it meant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Didn't know what it meant till we heard from people that yelled over the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they had relatives that are waiting for them, people that were working by the crematorium, people that were working for the [GERMAN] commander.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They told them what was happening and, you know, and they told them what to do and what not to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not to pre-- not to say that they're sick, not to say that they haven't got the strength, you know, always to be with the-- with the stronger people, things like that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were only there a short time-- I don't remember, eight or 10 days or something like that-- and we were sent to Kaufering in Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first when we arrived, they were standing there with the dogs, with the whips.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, who couldn't run away fast enough was-- was beaten with that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were letting the dogs-- you know--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Get at some-- bite at some people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were so occupied with getting into the-- into that line and into the middle-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] exactly, you know, I really, truly don't recall--",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
